<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>责任；职责：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>accept</strong> / shoulder (a) <strong>responsibility</strong> 
承担/担起责任</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Taking responsibility for</strong> something that went wrong is a mark of great maturity. 
对做错的事负责是非常成熟的标志。</p><footer>2010 天津</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The media has a <strong>moral responsibility</strong> to report news truthfully. 
媒体有如实报道新闻的道德责任。</p><footer>人教⑧ – 2</footer></div></div>